<html>
	<head>
		<title>BCM_SETFILENAME</title>
	</head>
	<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
		<p><font color="#000000" size="4"><strong>BCM_SETFILENAME</strong></font></p>
		<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="3" width="100%">
			<tr>
				<td width="100%" bgcolor="#e6e6e6"><pre>BCM_SETFILENAME
	wParam = 0;
	lParam = ( LPARAM )( LPCTSTR )lpszFilename;</pre>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
		<p>Changes the name of the control contents.</p>
		<ul type="disc">
			<li>
				Returns non-zero for success and zero for failure</li>
		</ul>
		<dl>
			<dt><em>lpszFilename</em>
				<dd>
					This must point to a 0-terminated string containing the path. The control will 
					automatically check and setup the correct text class settings for the specified 
					path. This pointer must be valid or the message will fail.</dd>
		</dl>
	</body>
</html>
